OL,3,CManhunt underway after victim suffers
OL,4,Cserious gunshot injuries in Bristol
OL,6,FA manhunt is underway in Bristol after
OL,7,Fa man was seriously injured in a
OL,8,Fshooting in the Speedwell area of the
OL,9,Fcity.
OL,11,FAvon and Somerset Police are searching
OL,12,Ffor a man who left the scene on a
OL,13,Fblack and grey electric bike.
OL,15,FHe was described as being white, aged
OL,16,Fin his late teens or early twenties,
OL,17,Fof slim build, and about 6ft tall. He
OL,18,Fwas wearing a grey hoodie, black
OL,19,Ftrousers, and a balaclava.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
