OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775139066
OL,3,CManhunt underway after victim suffers
OL,4,Cserious gunshot injuries in Bristol
OL,6,FThe incident took place at around
OL,7,F1.45pm today (April 1) when a shot was
OL,8,Ffired at a car in Speedwell Road.
OL,10,FThe victim, a man in his twenties, was
OL,11,Ftaken to Southmead Hospital with
OL,12,Fserious injuries. Police say they are
OL,13,F"potentially life-changing".
OL,15,FNearby roads were quickly sealed off
OL,16,Fand a number of local schools - Two
OL,17,FMile Hill School and Bristol Brunel
OL,18,FAcademy - were put in lockdown to
OL,19,Fensure the safety of children.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
