PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775139066
OL,3,CManhunt underway after victim suffers
OL,4,Cserious gunshot injuries in Bristol
OL,6,FChief Inspector James Clements said:
OL,7,F"I know this incident will be
OL,8,Fincredibly concerning, however we are
OL,9,Fdeploying significant resources,
OL,10,Fincluding a National Police Air
OL,11,FService helicopter and our specially-
OL,12,Ftrained firearms officers, as we work
OL,13,Fto locate the person responsible.
OL,15,F"The victim has been taken to hospital
OL,16,Fwhere he is being treated for an
OL,17,Finjury that's potentially life-
OL,18,Fchanging, but not believed to be life-
OL,19,Fthreatening. His family have been
OL,20,Finformed and will be kept updated as
OL,21,Four investigation progresses.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
