OL,3,CManhunt underway after victim suffers
OL,4,Cserious gunshot injuries in Bristol
OL,6,F"There is likely to be a significant
OL,7,Fpolice presence in the area over the
OL,8,Fcoming days while our investigation
OL,9,Fcontinues. Neighbourhood officers will
OL,10,Falso be carrying out extra patrols and
OL,11,Fanyone with any concerns can speak
OL,12,Fwith them about these."
